# BDS (Buzzle Design System) 사용 가이드

MUI를 기반으로 확장된 디자인 시스템. 완전한 TypeScript 지원.

## 기본 설정

```tsx
import { ThemeProvider } from '@mui/material/styles';
import { CssBaseline, Container } from '@mui/material';
import { bdsTheme, Button, Text, Input } from '@buzzle/bds';

export const App = () => (
	<ThemeProvider theme={bdsTheme}>
		<CssBaseline />
		<Container>
			<Text variant="h1" gradient>Buzzle Design System</Text>
			<Input label="이메일" placeholder="이메일을 입력해주세요" />
			<Button variant="contained">시작하기</Button>
		</Container>
	</ThemeProvider>
);
```

## Atoms 컴포넌트

### Button
- `variant`: `"contained"` | `"outlined"`
- `size`: `"small"` | `"medium"` | `"large"`
- `fullWidth`, `disabled`: boolean

### Input
- `label`, `placeholder`: string
- `type`: `"text"` | `"password"` | `"email"` | `"number"`
- `helperText`, `errorMessage`, `successMessage`: string

### Text
- `variant`: `"largeTitle"` | `"title1"` ~ `"caption2"`
- `gradient`: boolean, `fontWeight`: `"regular"` | `"medium"` | `"semibold"` | `"bold"`
- `color`: `"title"` | `"base"` | `"summary"` | `"subtitle"` | `"link"` 등

### Link
- `href`: string, `target`: `"_blank"` | `"_self"` 등

### Logo
- `size`: `"small"` | `"medium"` | `"large"`

### IconButton
- `size`: `"small"` | `"medium"` | `"large"`, `disabled`: boolean

## Molecules 컴포넌트

### BarGraph / LineGraph / PieGraph / DonutGraph
- `data`: 배열, `width`: number, `height`: number

### NavBar
- `logo`: ReactNode, `menuItems`: `Array<{label, href}>`

### Table
- `columns`: `Array<{header, accessorKey}>`, `data`: `Array<object>`

### FaqItem
- `question`: string, `answer`: string

## 디자인 토큰

색상 네이밍: `bds.token.color.[mode].[category].[variant]`

**라이트 모드 주요 색상:**
- Primary: `#6174FB`, Secondary: `#F34541`
- Success: `#15D267`, Information: `#3272FF`
- Warning: `#FF8210`, Danger: `#FC2B1C`

**그레이스케일:** `bds.token.color.gray.gray005` (#fafafa) ~ `gray100` (#0A0A0A)

